{{Top|leg}}
A '''negate''' was a type of duel practiced by the [[Phosphura Belt Pirates]] to settle internal disputes. The negate was a duel to the death. A [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] wanting to take the chair of the [[Pirate King/Legends|Pirate King or Queen]] could make a negate challenge, or a negate could be used to settle open hostilities between two pirate groups. It was by custom the subject of game wagers.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

To add a bit of excitement, negates could be fought in a "[[Fire Ring of Fornax]]."<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

